    "image" : "images/Pesang-Isda.jpg",
    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>2 pieces medium to large fish, sliced</li><li>2 bunches baby bok choy or pechay, cleaned and ends removed</li><li>2 cups rice washing</li><li>1 tablespoon salt</li><li>1 medium onion, quartered</li><li>½ cup green onions or onion leeks, sliced</li><li>¼ cup ginger, sliced and pounded</li><li>3 cloves garlic, minced</li><li>1 tablespoon fish sauce (patis)</li><li>½ teaspoon whole peppercorn</li><li>8 tablespoons cooking oil</li></ul>",
