    "image" : "images/Paksiw-na-Isda.jpg",
    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>2 pieces fish (about half a pound each), cleaned and scales removed</li><li>1 knob ginger, sliced and pounded</li><li>6 cloves garlic, skin removed</li><li>½ cup vinegar</li><li>1 cup water</li><li>1 medium onion, sliced</li><li>1 small bitter gourd, chopped (optional)</li><li>3 pieces finger chili</li><li>2 teaspoon salt</li><li>1 teaspoon whole peppercorn</li></ul>",
