    "ulam" : "Sinanglay na Tilapia Recipe",
    "image" : "images/Sinanglay-na-Tilapia.jpg",
    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>2 pieces medium tilapia, cleaned and scales removed</li><li>4 pieces wide bok choy (or pechay) leaves</li><li>4 cloves garlic, chopped</li><li>1 medium onion, diced</li><li>2 pieces medium tomatoes, diced</li><li>1 thumb ginger, chopped</li><li>3 pieces long green chili</li><li>1½ cups coconut milk</li><li>½ cup water</li><li>1 teaspoon salt</li></ul>",
