    "ulam" : "Steamed Fish with Mayonnaise",
    "image" : "images/Steamed-Fish-with-Mayonnaise.jpg",
    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>1 whole grouper (lapu-lapu), about 3 to 5 lbs.</li><li>1 medium red onion, minced</li><li>¾ cup minced red bell pepper</li><li>3 hard-boiled eggs, minced</li><li>¾ cup minced carrot</li><li>1½ cups mayonnaise</li><li>2 teaspoons sweet pickle relish</li><li>½ teaspoon salt</li><li>½ teaspoon ground black pepper</li><li>1 tablespoon salt, to rub all over the fish</li></ul>",
